As kvm_vcpu_ioctl(CPUState *cpu, int type, ...) takes CPUState *, this can be
tdx_vcpu_ioctl(CPUState *cpu, ) instead of void *.
I struggled to fin my mistake to pass "int vcpu_fd" to this function.
